Install
------

See 'INSTALL' file

Dependancies
-----------

This software requires zeromq, hiredis, boost C++ libraries, redis, protocol buffers (by google)  distributions installed. Please see 
corresponding documentation for installation and running.


Usage
----

For chatserver
chatServer -n <chatroomName> -i <rcv_ipaddress:port>-p <pub_ipaddress:port>

For client
  To send chats - chatClient -s -u <username> -i <server_ipaddress:port>
  To receive chats - chatClient -r -u <username> -i <server_listen_ipaddress:port>
